{"tid":1364131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如727元朗著到五顏六色咁戴頭盔行街","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T12:31:19.000Z","uid":272444,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc1bd1fb021666cc6a8cb8f8743171a9cc248496","tid":1364131,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地係嚟行街㗎咋，咩啫<br />\n但係聽講有遊行好危險呀，咁我唯有戴個頭盔保護自己啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然班友已經將黑衫有理冇理都當哂暴徒<br />\n咁不如今次就做一個良好市民嘅形象<br />\n件衫有以街坊就幾街坊，最好係啲老母級嘅核突logo T添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過為免有乜嘢突發情況，大家記得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">帶件黑色薄外套/黑色衫替換</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣先可以來去自如係咪先！！！！"},{"pid":"8c82e31d4e373e3f96ea3abae4cb0e9911c80015","tid":1364131,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:45:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c58571c5d7ef24c594d02e0e2db871883b62da52","tid":1364131,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:46:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d7a14279a5376c675802256d1778ba75be9b751","tid":1364131,"uid":163819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:46:27.000Z","msg":"元朗國服係白色"},{"pid":"e086cce4c4285bb7f92f78410cf42f9323790f9b","tid":1364131,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b02ea1bf28b67dfcc0703a6d8570118e9aba4d4","tid":1364131,"uid":272444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d7a14279a5376c675802256d1778ba75be9b751","tid":1364131,"uid":163819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:46:27.000Z","msg":"元朗國服係白色"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"我地係入元朗搵好嘢食嘅小市民咋<img src=\"/assets